  the right to education is a serious subject  there  is  shortage  of  teachers  in  every  state      about  14000  posts  of  teachers  are lying vacant in punjab  there are various reasons for drop out in education  there are  some  social  reasons  also    the  gap  between  a  primary  school  and  a  middle school is about 78 kms  there should be a shuttle service or bus service for such schools    teachers  are  deployed  for  works  relating  to  voting  and  census    the students  are  studying  in  unsafe  buildings    i  would  like  that  quality  of  education should be improved    